item.title: Enzo crashes into ocean at Targa Newfoundland 2011
item.description:
Enzo crashes into ocean at Targa Newfoundland 2011
An Enzo Ferrari heavily modified by Edo Competition crashes into ocean at Targa Newfoundland Rally 2011. Zahir Rana from ZR Auto was driving with Roland Linder Navigating. The Enzo crashed right after hitting a hard bump into gravel after a corner and lost control sending the car backwards off a ledge and into the ocean below.
